(1371, 173, 'about_us_left_text', 'That doesn’t mean it is worse or better. Of course, no. But this warm, sweet Hawaiian sun…sometimes we just need it so hard.<br>\r\nSo we found a solution. And you don’t even need to book a bungalow at the end of the day. Just order fresh Hawaiian Poke Bowls in Edinburgh from Papa Poke.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe were inspired by the Hawaiian Goddess of fruitfulness and prosperity called Papa. That is how we get our name and a piece of sun in each bowl. '),
(1372, 173, '_about_us_left_text', 'field_6386507135455'),
