(14, 'ppxo-pps-upgrade-paypal-payments-1', 'info', 'en_US', 'Get the latest PayPal extension for WooCommerce', 'Heads up! There’s a new PayPal on the block!<br /><br />Now is a great time to upgrade to our latest <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-paypal-payments/\" target=\"_blank\">PayPal extension</a> to continue to receive support and updates with PayPal.<br /><br />Get access to a full suite of PayPal payment methods, extensive currency and country coverage, and pay later options with the all-new PayPal extension for WooCommerce.', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2022-11-08 09:47:17', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info'),
